  "title": "AI Python Developer",
  "description": "<p>🚀 <strong>We’re Hiring: AI Python Developer – Agentic AI & LangGraph</strong> 🚀</p><p>Join a cutting-edge team building <strong>agentic AI workflows</strong> with LangGraph and LLMs!</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong><br />• Design and develop reusable agentic AI workflows using LangGraph<br />• Craft clear, effective prompts for diverse AI tasks<br />• Implement Agent-to-Agent (A2A) design patterns<br />• Write clean, production-grade Python code with pytest unit tests<br />• Manage version control with Git and automate CI/CD pipelines with GitLab</p><p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p><p><strong>Must-Have:</strong><br />• Strong prompt engineering skills for LLM control & output reliability, must have strong experience in prompt engineering, LangGraph, Python, Git.<br />• Experience building and maintaining LangGraph workflows & reusable components<br />• Proficiency in Python, including pytest unit testing<br />• Hands-on with Git & GitLab CI/CD for automated build, test, deploy pipelines</p><p><strong>Good-to-Have:</strong><br />• Experience in agentic AI system design & orchestration<br />• Understanding of A2A orchestration principles</p><p>💡 Ready to build the future of AI? Apply now and be part of the next-gen AI revolution!<br /></p><p>Please refer to U3’s Privacy Notice for Job Applicants/Seekers at</p><p>When you apply, you voluntarily consent to the collection, use and disclosure of your personal data for recruitment/employment and related purposes.</p><p><a href=\"https://u3infotech.com/privacy-notice-job-applicants/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://u3infotech.com/privacy-notice-job-applicants/. </a></p>",
